{"id":194795,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/自由光诚！-artists-speak-out《社论：致理查德-布兰森爵士》/","date":"2011-11-08T20:30:42Z","modified":"2011-11-08T20:30:42Z","title":"自由光诚！ | Artists Speak Out《社论：致理查德.布兰森爵士》","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zF4jM_etvcA/TrbujTA_LmI/AAAAAAAABEM/J0hhnMDLcf8/s1600/2011-11-07%2Bartistsspeakout.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"394\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zF4jM_etvcA/TrbujTA_LmI/AAAAAAAABEM/J0hhnMDLcf8/s400/2011-11-07%2Bartistsspeakout.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p>2011年11月5日，艺术家发声(Artists Speak Out)网站发表社论，题为：</p>\n<p><b><span>理查德.布兰森爵士必须呼吁释放中国盲人律师陈光诚</span></b></p>\n<p>在社论中谈到：理查德.布兰森爵士是一位人道主义者，对人权问题也很关注。他还是一位成功的影视制作商，并与在临沂拍摄的喜剧片《21岁派对》有关系。社论详细解释了陈光诚被中国政府迫害的经过和他一家目前的状况，要求理查德.布兰森爵士发出声音，还陈光诚自由。社论网页附一封给理查德.布兰森爵士的签名信。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://artistsspeakout.com/2011/11/editorial-sir-richard-branson-must-call-for-the-release-of-blind-chinese-lawyer-chen-guangcheng/\">原文链接（英语）</a></p>\n<p>艺术家发声推号 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/artistsspeakout\">@artistsspeakout</a></p>\n<p>理查德.布兰森爵士推号 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/richardbranson\">@richardbranson</a></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4889492683900327351-4020442896204166921?l=freecgc.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[9625,15095]}